{"tid":1599930,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"10月1日集中一區係左好睇，比國際睇","createTime":"2019-09-28T09:57:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-28T14:58:15.000Z","uid":13936,"like":33,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"a3f831c7a25b6cef27e517d124addcc5706c677e","tid":1599930,"uid":13936,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T09:57:30.000Z","msg":"屌<br />\n五年前講到今日都講到口臭<br />\n香港人抗爭永遠唔係想嬴<br />\n只係想好睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咩國際報導 咩好睇 <br />\n1百萬好睇未  2百萬人好睇未?<br />\n仲有個論點好ON9，咩人多洗驚佢拉<br />\n屌你第一日訓醒? 你幾多人 都照啦 ，點解呀? <br />\n因為劇本根本就係咁<br />\n港島行 -&gt; 行到金鐘佔路- &gt; 攻下政總 -&gt; 水炮車 TG 射下<br />\n速龍黎 -&gt; 成班大撤退 -&gt; 清場到老銅 -&gt; 拉人 -&gt; 完<br />\n咁就玩撚完10月一日喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n過去幾個月 成撚日話要好睇 要多人 要和理非<br />\n做左好多次啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咩叫兄弟爬山<br />\n人地五區咪五區 ，你咪你行港島<br />\n連登仔口講一套  實質就打壓其他行動POST<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n之前打壓街頭 捧機場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢家就打壓五區 捧港島<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"189dc421334c057610410125079718f26fa4760a","tid":1599930,"uid":13936,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T09:58:23.000Z","msg":"人多 佢地敢拉?<br />\n<br />\n呢班仆街講埋D 鳩野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 講呢句既人 敢唔敢企係前線第一個呀"},{"pid":"65f5df38cf4c970eef13921310ca312a8a9f38f1","tid":1599930,"uid":97776,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-2